# Project: City Explorer

## Description
An immersive 3D city exploration experience that allows users to walk, fly, or observe procedurally generated cities from any angle. Users should feel like they're exploring a living, breathing city with diverse architecture and atmospheric lighting.

## Technical Stack
- Modern web application
- 3D graphics with smooth performance
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile
- Type-safe development environment

## Core Requirements
- Real-time 3D rendering at 60fps on modern hardware
- Instant startup with no installation required
- Works in all modern browsers
- Saves user preferences and locations
- Supports keyboard, mouse, and touch controls